# Build output. Regenerated by `npm run build`; Cloudflare Workers Builds runs
# the build itself and uploads ./dist (see wrangler.jsonc `assets.directory`),
# so nothing here belongs in git. This used to be `/dist/index.html`, which
# ignored only the entry file and let the hashed bundles and the copy of
# public/ get committed by accident.
